  <!-- ============ STATS BAR ============ -->
  <section class="stats stats--with-image">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-bar-grid">
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">$250K-$5M+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Working RIA principal income range from junior principal at $50M-$150M AUM ($250K-$500K W-2 + K-1) through mid-tier principal at $150M-$500M AUM ($500K-$1.5M) to established principal at $500M-$2B+ AUM ($1.5M-$5M+) reflecting AUM-based recurring fee revenue capacity</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">8-12x ARR</div>
            <div class="stat-label">RIA practice valuation methodology typically 8-12x annual recurring revenue (ARR) or 2-3x revenue in active PE-backed consolidator transaction market. Practice valuations at multi-year highs driving substantial consolidator transaction volume</div>
